premise_source_doc_sentence: Amir Davidson  (  stage-named Amir Derakh  )  ,  (  born June 20 , 1963  )  is an American musician .
He is currently the guitarist and the synthesizer player for the band Julien-K , and guitarist for the band Dead by Sunrise .
He was once a guitar synthesizer player in the rock band Orgy , and has also played guitar in the bands Rough Cutt and Jailhouse .
Amir Davidson  (  stage-named Amir Derakh  )  ,  (  born June 20 , 1963  )  is an American musician .
The band consists of Linkin Park lead singer Chester Bennington , Amir Derakh , Ryan Shuck , Brandon Belsky , Elias Andra , and Anthony `` Fu '' Valcic from Julien-K and Orgy .

Out of Ashes is the debut studio album by American rock band Dead by Sunrise , which consists of Linkin Park lead vocalist Chester Bennington and Amir Derakh , Ryan Shuck , Anthony ` Fu ' Valcic , Brandon Belsky , and Elias Andra of Julien-K .
In addition to being an oboist , Paul Dombrecht is active as conductor and artistic director of the baroque orchestra Il Fondamento , the wind ensemble Octophoros and the Paul Dombrecht Consort .
